node.text:
I made a tiktok video about my PCOS & I’ve been flooded with DMs about how I cleared my skin & deal with my symptoms. I figured it would be easier to just sit down and chat about my whole experience. I didn’t feel it was necessary to make this a whole production with edits so enjoy me rambling on for 10 minutes. I want to be as real as I can with y’all. I will still respond to all the DMs that I can. I hope this helps & please message me with any other questions. If you’re struggling right now, I PROMISE it will get better 💓💞
Thank you to @esthylexi for changing my life & helping me get my skin back! #pcos #pcosawareness #pcosfighter #acnepositivity #skincare #skincaretips

node.text: My baby is 12 weeks old! Her favorite thing to do is eat people and stick her tongue out. She still hates pacifiers but is desperately trying to suck her thumb. She loves sitting up and trying to stand. Where did my little newborn go? 🥺❤️

node.text:
#ad Did you know that @cheerios is and has always been made from oats?!?! Im so excited to share that i have partnered with Cheerios to celebrate the 80th Anniversary of the iconic brand! Cheerios is going back to CheeriOats for a limited time to remind people Cheerios is made with oats! Cheerios has always been about families and creating memories together. #cheerios80thsweepstakes 

 Cheerios will always remind me of my grandparents. From as early as I can remember, every morning waking up at their house my Nawnie would set up my little tray in the living room and bring me a bowl of Cheerios. I would look to my right and there was my Poppy with his bowl of Cheerios in his chair. He would put on the morning cartoons and we would enjoy our Cheerios together. It’s a memory that I’ll cherish forever. Now 20+ years later and miles apart, I can still enjoy my morning Cheerios with my Poppy over FaceTime! 

Now I want to hear your Cheerios story! Share your story with the hashtag #CheeriosSweepstakes on Twitter or Instagram for a chance to win a customized Cheerios box! Enter by August 1, 2021. Open to US residents only, 18+. Full Rules at: www.cheerios.com/Cheerios80thSweepstakes 
#cheerios80thsweepstakes #cheerios
